	measure passcircu|totPass = ```
			VAR selected_date = CALCULATE(
			                    MAX(balancetenew[data]), 
			                    ALLSELECTED(balancetenew[data])
			                  )
			RETURN
			    DIVIDE(
			        SUMX(
			            FILTER('balancetenew', 
			                'balancetenew'[data] = selected_date
			            ),
			            'Medidas_balancetenew'[ssomapasscircu_actual_month]
			        ),
			        SUMX(
			            FILTER('balancetenew', 
			                'balancetenew'[data] = selected_date
			            ),
			            'Medidas_balancetenew'[totpassivo II]
			        )
			    )
			```
