	measure 'totpassivo II' = ```
			
			VAR UltimoDiaTrimestre = 
			    LASTDATE(
			        DATESINPERIOD(
			            dCalendario[data], 
			            MAX(dCalendario[data]), -3, 
			            QUARTER
			        )
			    )
			VAR UltimoMesTrimestre = 
			    EOMONTH(UltimoDiaTrimestre,-1)+1
			
			VAR _passcir = [ssomapasscircu]
			VAR _passncir = [ssomapassncirculante]
			
			    RETURN
			    CALCULATE(
			_passcir +  
			    IF(_passncir < 0
			    , _passncir * -1
			    , _passncir)
			    ,dCalendario[data] >= UltimoMesTrimestre && dCalendario[data] <= UltimoDiaTrimestre)
			```
		formatString: #,0.00
		lineageTag: 38ada53b-fc37-4f5e-b891-4772d796c9c5

